打拳既成日吹噓泰臣<br />\n阿里呀Robinson個班心諗笑撚死我</blockquote><br />\nAli<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fee87a0eeb9afbb515f983f080a491a1d64a582","tid":168482,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:50:18.000Z","msg":"佢同浪客劍心個尖角一樣，只要不停閃開佢既攻擊，佢自己會抝柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8de0df113644dbbe9e7c2726cec1c0a6b6e0e2","tid":168482,"uid":85011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/5db00076ff39c870c2f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F5db00076ff39c870c2f&h=f9e8770b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fzSIO6o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfzSIO6o.gif&h=d3f3e7ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說到拳擊這項運動，即使是不懂不喜歡拳擊的朋友們也能第一個想到泰臣吧。沒錯，邁克&middot;泰臣（Michael Gerard Tyson）這位出生於1966年的黑人在拳壇上的影響絕對可以稱得上是前無古人後無來者的存在。<br />\n<br />\n泰臣出生於美國紐約，曾經的職業重量級職業拳擊運動員，兩次世界重量級冠軍，曾被譽世界上最好的拳手之一。泰臣的巔峰時期以自己出色的身體素質和高超的出拳技巧加上其毀滅性的拳擊風格擊敗了無數著名拳手。<br />\n而其職業生涯的終結也是因為其自身缺乏訓練和曾兩度入獄而畫上了句號，2005年的6月11日泰臣的退役賽對陣學徒拳擊手凱文&middot;麥克布萊德，也以失敗告終，至此泰臣的職業生涯正式結束。<br />\nADVERTISEMENT<br />\n泰臣擁有<span style=\"color: red;\">180mm的身高</span>和180mm的臂展。力量方面：卧推132公斤、深蹲463公斤，右拳800千克、左拳500千克。而在力量測試儀的測試中泰臣的打擊力度在500-800公斤，所以科學上講只要位置合適，泰臣一拳打死一頭成年公牛的可能性是存在的。<br />\n泰臣職業生涯一共50次勝利6次失敗，其中兩次對手直接棄權，44次KO對手，24次只用第一回合就將對手擊敗。在如此恐怖的數據下如果泰臣的巔峰時期再能延長一點沒有那些負面時間的出現，以泰臣的無解打法超越阿里或許也不是不可能的事。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係一嚟睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />短過我條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n味必<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26055edc00dfa07da9eaa51e63066683ab4da8f6","tid":168482,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:59:37.000Z","msg":"佢果6敗 好似有5敗都係出獄後輸?"},{"pid":"e01e1f7d2147d2bf7b3b0cb2f86e7956996d5c3f","tid":168482,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T01:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢同浪客劍心個尖角一樣，只要不停閃開佢既攻擊，佢自己會抝柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尖角本身都好快 但劍心更快者<br />\n一般人都避唔到尖角啦<br />\n佢識瞬移架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c098a986d19b09726ee6a203b2a9ed472c31b3ed","tid":168482,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T01:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問好耐，Ali好打d定泰臣好打D呢其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nali啲神之閃避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇全盛時期戰績數據應該泰臣贏面大d"},{"pid":"8a77301c399120b2d73d0f7765b28d5fcd4e07fd","tid":168482,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問好耐，Ali好打d定泰臣好打D呢其實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nali啲神之閃避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇全盛時期戰績數據應該泰臣贏面大d</blockquote><br />\n睇數據星如仲勁啦"},{"pid":"925978c68f85b96e33a6360d6d2d1710930199a9","tid":168482,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T01:11:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>葉問中甘多拳都未死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YEWVYBZAGgU&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYEWVYBZAGgU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D102&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpg